Hazel V. REIDENBACH, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. A. I. NAMM & SON, Defendant-Appellee. Hazel V. REIDENBACH, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. KOPS BROTHERS, Inc., Defendant-Appellee. No. 39. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Oct. 17, 1938. Hattff & Warland, of New York City ÍWm. E. Warland, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Merrell E. Clark, of New York City (William J. Barnes, of New York City, of counsel), for appellees.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decrees, 25 F.Supp. 235, affirmed.
